Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有足够的时间和胆量\N{\ren}If you've got the time and the stomach for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我这儿有个故事要讲给你听\N{\ren}I've got a story for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,关于魔法与女巫的传说\N{\ren}A tale of magic and witches,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,关于冒险与怪物的奇谭\N{\ren}of quests and of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,关于善与恶的较量\N{\ren}Of good and of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但别搞错了\N{\ren}But make no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是什么童话故事\N{\ren}This is no fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会有幸福美满的结局\N{\ren}And there are no happy endings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你熟悉的那个世界早已消亡\N{\ren}The world you know is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在远古大战的烈焰中灰飞烟灭\N{\ren}consumed by the flames of a great war long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当死亡如雨点般从天而降时\N{\ren}when death rained from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如今只剩下这片"失落之地"\N{\ren}All that's left now are the Lost Lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,盘踞着在阴影中扭曲蠕动的怪物\N{\ren}filled with twisted creatures that dwell in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,残存的人类龟缩在最后一座城市里\N{\ren}What remains of humanity takes refuge in a single city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前 有位神秘女巫\N{\ren}Long ago, a mysterious witch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,灰艾丽斯 从失落之地现身\N{\ren}Gray Alys, emerged from the Lost Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们相遇的故事\N{\ren}This is the story of how we met
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也是她拯救我们两人的传奇\N{\ren}and how she saved the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,停下你们手里的活!\N{\ren}Stop your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我停下!\N{\ren}Stop your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是违抗教会的下场\N{\ren}Let this be an example to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看谁还敢忤逆圣教\N{\ren}No one shall defy the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,人们都说只要找灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}They say you can buy anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,任何愿望都能用钱买到\N{\ren}you might desire from Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但最好别这么做\N{\ren}But it's better not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可人们还是前仆后继找你帮忙\N{\ren}And still the people seek your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们愚昧无知\N{\ren}They're ignorant, uneducated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有穷有富 但都走投无路\N{\ren}Some are poor, some rich. All are desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不拒绝任何人\N{\ren}I refuse no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知道教会怎么评价你这种人吗?\N{\ren}Do you know what the church says about the likes of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定要开始说教了\N{\ren}I'm sure you're going to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,说你是恶魔的使徒\N{\ren}That you are of the devil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,铲除你是我们的神圣职责\N{\ren}and it's our duty to root you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,以山底城统治者\N{\ren}In the name of the Overlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,圣教大祭司\N{\ren}ruler of the City Under The Mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,至高领主之名\N{\ren}High Priest of the Faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我宣判你 灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}I sentence you, Gray Alys,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,处以绞刑\N{\ren}to death by hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,忏悔吧 魔女\N{\ren}Repent, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是怎么了?\N{\ren}What is happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经被蛊惑了\N{\ren}You cannot be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,成了女巫的奴隶\N{\ren}You're a slave to the witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,给我追杀她\N{\ren}Hunt her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 集合 - 遵命大人\N{\ren}- To me. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现身吧 魔女\N{\ren}Show yourself, witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,动手啊\N{\ren}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,快动手\N{\ren}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妖女!\N{\ren}Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找到你的\N{\ren}I will find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你将在炼狱中焚烧\N{\ren}You will burn in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,女巫！你他妈就该下地狱被烧成灰！\N{\ren}You will burn in hell, witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个绞不死的女巫\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个绞不死的女巫\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang.
