Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个绞不死的女巫\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个绞不死的女巫\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个绞不死的女巫\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那个绞不死的女巫\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一个人想伏击另一个人\N{\ren}If a man wanted to ambush another man,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是绝佳地点\N{\ren}this would be the perfect spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他眼睛还没适应黑暗就扑上去\N{\ren}Jump him while his eyes were still adjusting to the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最好再带三四个帮手\N{\ren}Maybe even bring three, four friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,确保万无一失\N{\ren}Make sure the job got done right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这玩意儿从来就没好使过\N{\ren}This thing has never worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个永远不会失手\N{\ren}But this never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听出我的脚步声了?\N{\ren}Did you recognize my footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是你的善意\N{\ren}No. Your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市越来越堕落\N{\ren}This city gets worse and worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但你始终如此慷慨\N{\ren}but you have always been so generous
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,从我小时候就是\N{\ren}ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只对你如此\N{\ren}Only to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你从不向我索取任何东西\N{\ren}You never ask anything of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪\N{\ren}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的声音和我年轻时听到的一模一样\N{\ren}You sound no different to when I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但你现在应该和我一样老了吧\N{\ren}but you must be old now like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,更老\N{\ren}Older.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老得多\N{\ren}Much older.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是杰雷斯 -守望团团长\N{\ren}- I'm Jerais. - Captain of the Overwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是领主派你来的?\N{\ren}Have you come on behalf of the Overlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还是他的王后?\N{\ren}Or perhaps his queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么风把您吹来见我这等人?\N{\ren}What brings you to visit one like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,据说只要付出代价 你就能实现愿望\N{\ren}It is said that for a price, you grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想买什么?\N{\ren}What do you wish to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,退下\N{\ren}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这不妥\N{\ren}I'm not sure if that is wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有人说你来自失落之地\N{\ren}Some say you came from the Lost Lands
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,知晓那里栖息的生物\N{\ren}and that you know the things that live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗的 非自然的异类\N{\ren}Dark, unnatural things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你想从我这里得到的?\N{\ren}Is this what you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听童话故事?\N{\ren}To tell you fairy tales?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要获得化身野兽的力量 灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}I want from you the power to become a beast, Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,超越凡人之躯 吓到你了?\N{\ren}To be more than human. Does that shock you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我见识太多 早就不容易被吓到了\N{\ren}I have seen too much to be shocked so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你能卖给我变形术的秘诀?\N{\ren}So you can sell me the secret of shapeshifting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,变成狼?\N{\ren}To a wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定想要所求之物?\N{\ren}Are you certain you want what you ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你得到的东西可能会让你后悔\N{\ren}You might not be happy with what you receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这不关你的事.- 我不得不帮忙.\N{\ren}- This is not your concern. - I am compelled to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我警告所有来找我的人.- 我不是"所有人"\N{\ren}- But I warn all who come to me. - I'm not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯.- 你会接受我的提议吗?\N{\ren}- Mm. - Will you accept my offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不拒绝任何人.我会雇个猎手\N{\ren}I refuse no one. I'll hire a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找到变形者夺取它的力量\N{\ren}We'll find you a shapeshifter and take its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,给我到月圆之夜的时间\N{\ren}Give me until the full moon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就能给你想要的东西\N{\ren}and I will bring you what you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪?\N{\ren}Where will you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,失落之地\N{\ren}To the Lost Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了杰瑞斯?\N{\ren}What is it, Jerais?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的来者不拒?\N{\ren}Do you refuse no one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来者不拒\N{\ren}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那就收下这个当报酬.我要为自己买愿望\N{\ren}Then accept it as my payment. I wish to buy for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这时计在我家族传承了数代\N{\ren}This timepiece has been in my family for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是我最珍贵的宝物\N{\ren}It's my most valuable possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么愿望?\N{\ren}And what do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你让她失败\N{\ren}I want you to fail her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,守望者立誓效忠\N{\ren}The Overwatch is sworn to loyalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你却背叛女王\N{\ren}yet you betray your queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我很忠诚\N{\ren}I am loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我比她更清楚什么对她有益\N{\ren}I know what's good for her better than she knows herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她追求的力量会毁了她\N{\ren}This power that she seeks will destroy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想帮忙\N{\ren}I only want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谎杰瑞斯\N{\ren}You lie, Jerais.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你酸味都快溢出来了\N{\ren}You reek of jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不和你争辩\N{\ren}I will not argue with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,若不愿与我交易我就离开\N{\ren}If you will not sell to me, I will leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不拒绝任何人\N{\ren}I refuse no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你会得到想要的\N{\ren}You shall have what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,呃啊!\N{\ren}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,呃啊!\N{\ren}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么?\N{\ren}What is it you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\ren}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\ren}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你又尿裤子了?\N{\ren}Did you wet yourself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不能用铃铛吗\N{\ren}Can't you use the bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老不死的蠢货?\N{\ren}you old disgusting fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,伟大的霸主啊\N{\ren}The mighty Overlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,难以相信这些都是你建造的\N{\ren}Hard to believe you built all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们居然还畏惧你\N{\ren}And that they still fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不过是个肮脏的猪猡\N{\ren}You're nothing more than a filthy pig,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,和所有男人一样\N{\ren}just like all men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的女王?\N{\ren}My queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所有男人,除了一个\N{\ren}All men, except for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,先别走\N{\ren}Don't leave yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须走了\N{\ren}I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他们没发现我\N{\ren}Before they see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不能留在这里\N{\ren}I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快点回来.求你了\N{\ren}Hurry back. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\ren}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\ren}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,站住！霸主麾下办事！\N{\ren}Halt, in the name of the Overlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这鬼鬼祟祟干什么?\N{\ren}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,酒越烈\N{\ren}The stronger the spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,人越菜\N{\ren}the weaker the senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们走一趟\N{\ren}You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别动!\N{\ren}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这瓶还剩半壶呢\N{\ren}That was half full.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你是荒野猎人 常年在失落之地游荡\N{\ren}I hear you're a hunter, that you travel the Lost Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要这种人才\N{\ren}I have use of such a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老子是来打牌的 不是来唠嗑的\N{\ren}Came here to play cards, not to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,全押\N{\ren}All in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在愿意开口了?\N{\ren}You ready to talk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,报上名来\N{\ren}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯\N{\ren}Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找个向导\N{\ren}I'm looking for a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,熟悉失落之地的那种\N{\ren}Someone who knows the Lost Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我出场费很贵 - 老子有的是钱\N{\ren}- I'm expensive. - I have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看得出来 毕竟你兜里大半都是我的钱\N{\ren}I know you do. Most of it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你配得上这个价吗?\N{\ren}Are you worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是不配 你还会坐在这跟我扯淡?\N{\ren}Would you be here talking to me if I wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,失落之地可不是城里人该去的地方\N{\ren}The Lost Lands are no place for city folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说?\N{\ren}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为城里人都是弱鸡\N{\ren}Because they're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我像弱鸡吗?\N{\ren}Do I look weak to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\ren}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,出了这道城墙 什么王法\N{\ren}Outside these walls, the laws of the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,人伦 甚至自然法则 统统不作数\N{\ren}of man, even of nature, they don't apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不管你在城里多牛逼\N{\ren}So whoever you think you are here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,到了荒野就是个拖油瓶\N{\ren}out there you'd just be a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不如打个赌\N{\ren}Let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我拖你后腿\N{\ren}If I ever slow you down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你随时可以把我当累赘扔掉\N{\ren}you have my permission to leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,反之亦然\N{\ren}And I'll do the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥非要出城?\N{\ren}Why do you want to leave the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找一个能变身野兽的男人\N{\ren}I'm looking for a man who can turn into a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,男人都是禽兽\N{\ren}All men are beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但并非都是怪物\N{\ren}But not all men are monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你在找变形者\N{\ren}You're looking for a shapeshifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对 必须在他老巢宰了他才能夺取力量\N{\ren}Yes. I need to kill it in its lair to take its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是听过这号人物\N{\ren}I've heard of such a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道什么情报?\N{\ren}What do you know of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,人称巨狼萨尔多\N{\ren}They call him Sardor, the Great Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个萨尔多住在哪?\N{\ren}Where does this man, this Sardor, live?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,骷髅河地界\N{\ren}In a place called Skull River.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,骷髅河...\N{\ren}Skull River.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正是我要去的地方\N{\ren}That's my destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方没几个人去过\N{\ren}Not many have travelled there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也没人活着回来 - 带路...\N{\ren}- No one's come back. - Guide me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这玩意儿归你了\N{\ren}and this can be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听说过这玩意 头回见实物\N{\ren}I've heard of these. Never seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要了\N{\ren}I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你偷我的那枚金币\N{\ren}And the coin you stole from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等我到了骷髅河自会结账\N{\ren}You'll receive your payment once I get to Skull River.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友?\N{\ren}Friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人没啥朋友\N{\ren}Yeah, I don't have many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此彼此\N{\ren}Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抄家伙!\N{\ren}Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\ren}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,给我搜\N{\ren}Find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那贱人弄死了我的蛇!\N{\ren}That bitch killed my snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,无人可违逆教会\N{\ren}No one shall defy the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是教会用律法守护着\N{\ren}It is the Church that protects the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市的安宁\N{\ren}of this city with its laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是教会让无信者心怀敬畏\N{\ren}The Church that puts fear into the hearts of the godless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.77,0:23:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是教会将迷失之地的\N{\ren}The Church that keeps the evils
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,邪恶阻挡在外\N{\ren}of the Lost Lands at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我等乃神的使者\N{\ren}We are God's instruments,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,降世护佑尔等免受邪祟侵扰\N{\ren}placed on this earth to protect you from such evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,追捕罪人、异端与女巫\N{\ren}Hunt down the sinners, the heretics, and the witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,押来见我者必有重赏\N{\ren}Bring them to me and you shall be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.51,0:24:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,灰艾丽斯带着个男人\N{\ren}Gray Alys, with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.74,0:24:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,两人一同出城了\N{\ren}They left the city together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,民众已不再敬畏我们\N{\ren}The people lose respect for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.15,0:24:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"绞不死的女巫"\N{\ren}"The witch that will not hang."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.55,0:24:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,灰艾丽斯成了他们反抗的象征\N{\ren}Gray Alys has become a symbol of their defiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.49,0:24:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她留你在十字架上苟活是在羞辱教会\N{\ren}She left you alive on that cross to humiliate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.26,0:24:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这女人必须死\N{\ren}This woman needs to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.13,0:24:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还有件事\N{\ren}There is another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.78,0:25:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是? - 你来说\N{\ren}- What is this? - Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.85,0:25:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,快说\N{\ren}Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.36,0:25:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有对男女去找过她\N{\ren}A man and a woman went to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.03,0:25:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我听见名字了\N{\ren}I heard their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.43,0:25:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是杰瑞斯和女王\N{\ren}It was Jerais and the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.80,0:25:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,若女王与异端勾结\N{\ren}If the queen has been consorting with a heretic,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.44,0:25:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是自寻死路\N{\ren}it would be her downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,确保女巫上绞架前\N{\ren}Make sure the witch makes a full confession
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.01,0:25:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,招供彻底\N{\ren}before she hangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.05,0:25:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不许出错\N{\ren}No mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.22,0:26:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙\N{\ren}No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.29,0:26:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,头回见男人为条蛇动感情\N{\ren}Never saw a man get emotional about a snake before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.30,0:26:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谁动感情了 只是...\N{\ren}I'm not emotional, it just--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.10,0:26:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是条极品好蛇 真的\N{\ren}It was a damn good snake, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.41,0:26:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,给 撞针掰直了 现在应该好使\N{\ren}Here. The pin was bent. It should work well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.58,0:26:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你别再拿它砸人脑袋\N{\ren}As long as you stop beating men to death with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.52,0:27:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明人可能会选择半路干掉雇主\N{\ren}A clever man might choose to kill his client on the road
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.92,0:27:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,提前拿钱跑路\N{\ren}and take his payment early.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.63,0:27:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜没人说过我聪明\N{\ren}But no one ever accused me of being a clever man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.22,0:28:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯的据点到了\N{\ren}This is Ross's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.19,0:28:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他和妹妹玛拉都是我的老相识\N{\ren}He and his sister Mara are old friends of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.69,0:28:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\ren}Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.30,0:28:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯\N{\ren}Hey, Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.13,0:28:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真好\N{\ren}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.17,0:28:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有玛拉\N{\ren}And Mara.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.81,0:29:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还是这么热情 - 好久不见\N{\ren}- Welcoming as ever. - It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.34,0:29:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你养尊处优了\N{\ren}You look soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.01,0:29:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看来城里日子过得滋润\N{\ren}The City has been treating you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.98,0:29:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 女人也没少睡吧 - 嗯\N{\ren}- As have the women, I bet. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.59,0:29:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦吼!\N{\ren}Ooh-ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.43,0:29:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是我的旅伴灰雅莉丝\N{\ren}Uh, meet my traveling companion, Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.26,0:29:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\ren}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.27,0:29:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯的友人就是我们的朋友\N{\ren}A friend of Boyce is a friend of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.31,0:29:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要从萨铎那里获得的力量\N{\ren}Gray Alys: The powers I want from Sardor
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.08,0:29:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在他的巢穴里最为强大\N{\ren}will be strongest in his lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.21,0:29:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,到骷髅河还要多久?\N{\ren}How much longer till Skull River?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.35,0:29:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一周 或许更久 - 我需要他保持狼形\N{\ren}- A week, maybe longer. - I need him as a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.45,0:29:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以得赶在月圆前抵达\N{\ren}So we need to get there before the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.25,0:29:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不简单\N{\ren}That won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.62,0:29:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是简单还用得着你？\N{\ren}Well, if it was easy, I wouldn't need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.63,0:30:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的捷径是沿着铁轨走\N{\ren}The only way would be following the train tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.07,0:30:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,隧道能穿山而过\N{\ren}The tunnels cut through the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.94,0:30:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然危险 但能省一两天\N{\ren}It'd be dangerous, but we'd save maybe a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.12,0:30:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.79,0:30:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你该再来一杯\N{\ren}You need another drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.92,0:30:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,每次见我都这么开心\N{\ren}Always happy to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.93,0:30:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这破地方太无聊了\N{\ren}It gets boring out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.59,0:30:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她可真走运\N{\ren}Lucky her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.50,0:30:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那个跟你同行的女人\N{\ren}So, who is this woman
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.90,0:30:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么来头?\N{\ren}you're traveling with?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.30,0:30:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,少打听\N{\ren}None of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.14,0:30:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢她?\N{\ren}Do you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.71,0:30:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不像对你这样的喜欢\N{\ren}Not the way I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\ren}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.78,0:30:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,又要等一年才能见到你?\N{\ren}Will it be another year until I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.12,0:30:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如果我还能活着\N{\ren}Mm. If I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.46,0:31:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在失落之地 一年足够沧海桑田\N{\ren}One year--a long time in the Lost Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.30,0:31:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,人来人往\N{\ren}You come, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.24,0:31:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你一无所知\N{\ren}I don't know anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.34,0:31:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道什么?\N{\ren}What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.61,0:31:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会感到孤独吗?\N{\ren}Do you ever get lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.81,0:31:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,会\N{\ren}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.98,0:31:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让我告诉你什么是孤独\N{\ren}Let me tell you about loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.35,0:31:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想象有个孩子...\N{\ren}Think of a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.39,0:31:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,置身黑暗\N{\ren}out there in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.49,0:31:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,惊恐万状\N{\ren}Afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.22,0:31:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,父母被人活活打死...\N{\ren}His parents beaten to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.09,0:31:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就在他眼前\N{\ren}right in front of his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.90,0:31:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩在荒原流浪\N{\ren}The boy travels the wasteland,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.57,0:31:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,躲避着亡命之徒\N{\ren}hiding from the outlaws
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.17,0:31:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,白天躲避掠夺者,\N{\ren}and the raiders during the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.84,0:31:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚对抗怪物和食尸鬼.\N{\ren}and the creatures and the ghouls at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.04,0:31:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,直到某天那个男孩长大成人,\N{\ren}Till one day that boy becomes a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.21,0:31:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,心肠和头脑都变得冷硬.\N{\ren}and his heart and his mind harden.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.22,0:32:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但他仍继续孤独前行,\N{\ren}But still he travels on, silently,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.39,0:32:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕与人亲近唯恐失去.\N{\ren}scared to get close to anyone for fear of losing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.76,0:32:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是孤独.\N{\ren}That is loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.86,0:32:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小男孩就是你.\N{\ren}And that little boy was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.77,0:32:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不.放屁,当然不是.\N{\ren}No. Hell, no. Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.67,0:32:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子从没掉过一滴泪.\N{\ren}I've never cried a day in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.91,0:32:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本一点都不了解我.\N{\ren}You really don t know anything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.39,0:32:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是我们最后见到的友善面孔.\N{\ren}Those are the last friendly faces we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.46,0:32:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在前方只剩下失落之地了.\N{\ren}There's only the Lost Lands ahead of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.51,0:33:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么?\N{\ren}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.48,0:33:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,祈祷霸主早日归来.\N{\ren}Offering a prayer for the Overlord's swift return.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.51,0:33:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大主教,您的专列和大批\N{\ren}Patriarch, the train and a large contingent
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.42,0:33:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,执法者已经离城.\N{\ren}of your enforcers have left the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.29,0:33:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁批准的?-我.\N{\ren}- Who authorized this? - I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.69,0:33:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们去哪?-追捕女巫灰艾丽斯.\N{\ren}- Where are they going? - To catch the witch Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.96,0:33:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-她涉嫌异端罪.-你的人应该留守.\N{\ren}- She is wanted for heresy. - Your men are needed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.50,0:33:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,街上骚乱愈演愈烈.\N{\ren}There is growing unrest in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.10,0:33:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,您让我们陷入危险了,大主教.\N{\ren}You leave us vulnerable, Patriarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.20,0:33:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,巫术罪当处死,\N{\ren}Witchcraft is punishable by death,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.30,0:33:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,女巫及其同党皆不可赦.\N{\ren}both for the witch and all who consort with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.97,0:34:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎她或她的所作所为.\N{\ren}I do not care about her or what she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.61,0:34:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-为何如此?-休得质问.\N{\ren}- And why is that? - Do not question me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.98,0:34:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-我代表霸主发言.-恕我冒犯.\N{\ren}- I speak for the Overlord. - Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.32,0:34:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但您说得对,时局动荡.\N{\ren}But you are right, these are dangerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.12,0:34:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,霸主的掌控日渐衰弱.\N{\ren}The Overlord's hand is losing its grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.96,0:34:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我到处看到违抗之举.\N{\ren}I see defiance everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.69,0:34:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-还有流言.-什么流言?\N{\ren}- And there are rumors. - What rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.00,0:34:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不能.-什么流言?\N{\ren}- I cannot. - What rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.97,0:34:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,关于您的不忠.\N{\ren}Of your infidelity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.00,0:34:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,纯属谎言.\N{\ren}Nothing but lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没错.卑劣之徒的恶毒谗言.\N{\ren}Yes. Vile words spoken by the basest of tongues.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.98,0:34:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但即便在渣滓中,谎言也有力量.\N{\ren}But even amongst the scum and rabble, lies have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.62,0:34:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,王后犯有勾结女巫之罪.\N{\ren}The queen is guilty of consorting with a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.56,0:34:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在看清楚了.\N{\ren}I see it clearly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.26,0:34:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把灰艾丽斯和她的供词带来.\N{\ren}Bring me Gray Alys and her confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.49,0:34:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,余下由我处理.\N{\ren}I will do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.16,0:34:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,霸主命不久矣,\N{\ren}The Overlord is dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.00,0:35:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有子嗣,王后势单力薄.\N{\ren}and with no heir, the queen is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.77,0:35:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很快都城将迎来新纪元.\N{\ren}Soon, there will be a new day in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.60,0:35:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随新黎明到来的,会是新霸主.\N{\ren}And with the new dawn, a new Overlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.28,0:35:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!求求你!\N{\ren}Aah! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.62,0:35:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-天啊.-不!\N{\ren}- God. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.19,0:35:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的都说了!\N{\ren}I told you all I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!我发誓!\N{\ren}Aah! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.44,0:35:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不!不!不!\N{\ren}No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.64,0:35:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手!不要!\N{\ren}Stop! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.37,0:35:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,骷髅河!\N{\ren}Skull River!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.61,0:35:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就在那儿\N{\ren}That's where they're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.28,0:35:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,骷髅河!\N{\ren}Skull River!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.58,0:35:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就在那儿\N{\ren}That's where they're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.04,0:35:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,烧了它\N{\ren}Burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.68,0:36:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯 你在这有家人吗?\N{\ren}Do you have a family out here, Boyce?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.12,0:36:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有家吗?\N{\ren}A home?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.79,0:36:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,遗忘之地是个孤独的地方\N{\ren}The Lost Lands are a lonely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.89,0:36:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,城里也一样\N{\ren}The city, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.91,0:36:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫它裂隙城\N{\ren}They call it the Rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.71,0:36:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,前面有个安全渡河点\N{\ren}There's a place up ahead where we can make a safe crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.07,0:37:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,赛勒斯!\N{\ren}Sirus!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老头你在哪?\N{\ren}Where you at, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.18,0:37:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我朋友的缆车\N{\ren}That's my friend's cable car.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.51,0:37:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老赛勒斯收一枚银币就载人过河\N{\ren}Old Sirus will take us over for a silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.32,0:37:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对岸有他养的新马\N{\ren}He keeps fresh horses on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.52,0:37:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你付钱\N{\ren}You're paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.43,0:37:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,赛勒斯?\N{\ren}Sirus?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.97,0:37:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,赛勒斯?\N{\ren}Sirus?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.37,0:37:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在这等着\N{\ren}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.05,0:39:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯?\N{\ren}Boyce?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.45,0:39:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看来赛勒斯有访客了\N{\ren}Seems Sirus had visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.69,0:39:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也是\N{\ren}So do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.20,0:39:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就是博伊斯 那个猎魔人\N{\ren}So you're Boyce. The Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.30,0:39:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们问老头你是不是已经过河了\N{\ren}We asked the old man if you had already crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.51,0:39:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他嘴挺严\N{\ren}He wasn't very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.44,0:39:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直挺喜欢赛勒斯\N{\ren}I always liked Sirus.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.68,0:39:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你身边是谁啊 猎魔人?\N{\ren}Who is that with you, hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.92,0:39:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,收起你的巫术把戏 妖女\N{\ren}None of your tricks, witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.46,0:39:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你都不敢直视我们\N{\ren}You can't look us in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.22,0:39:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,交出她 饶你不死\N{\ren}Hand her over and we'll let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.73,0:39:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她脑袋可值钱\N{\ren}There's a bounty on her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.33,0:40:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 她先雇的我\N{\ren}Sorry, she hired me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.53,0:40:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你个老江湖还挺讲道义?\N{\ren}A man of principle. Who'd have thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.24,0:40:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,交人 或者一起死\N{\ren}Give us the witch or you both die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.39,0:40:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不交\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.92,0:40:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,与圣教会为敌者\N{\ren}No one shall defy the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.49,0:40:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们自称神的仆人?!这算哪门子神?!\N{\ren}You say you're servants of God?! What kind of God is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,复仇之神\N{\ren}The vengeful kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来找怪物\N{\ren}You came here looking for a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.44,0:40:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在找到了\N{\ren}Now you found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.95,0:40:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯...\N{\ren}Boyce...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.38,0:40:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了\N{\ren}Behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.25,0:40:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,见证奇迹吧\N{\ren}A resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.46,0:41:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.97,0:41:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯快走\N{\ren}Boyce, we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.64,0:41:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃!- 走!\N{\ren}- Argh! - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.66,0:42:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,快!\N{\ren}Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.27,0:43:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\ren}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.14,0:43:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呃!\N{\ren}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.72,0:43:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,切断缆绳！\N{\ren}Cut the cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.92,0:43:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快砍断缆绳!\N{\ren}Cut the cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.49,0:43:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快砍啊!\N{\ren}Cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.14,0:44:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,呃啊!\N{\ren}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.96,0:44:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,得往上爬!\N{\ren}We have to climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.37,0:45:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,动作快!\N{\ren}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.22,0:45:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\ren}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.49,0:46:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她为什么没杀我?\N{\ren}Why didn't she finish me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.06,0:46:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她尽力了\N{\ren}She tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.37,0:46:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是个女巫\N{\ren}A witch, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.50,0:46:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么过去?\N{\ren}How do we cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.44,0:46:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,得绕路走\N{\ren}We have to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.87,0:46:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就动身吧\N{\ren}Then let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.38,0:46:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会往山脉方向逃\N{\ren}They'll be headed for the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.08,0:46:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不,他们正走向地狱\N{\ren}No. Hell is where they're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.90,0:46:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗?\N{\ren}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.73,0:46:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,醉得厉害\N{\ren}Drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.24,0:46:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哼!\N{\ren}Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.84,0:46:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.78,0:46:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才差点就死了\N{\ren}I could've died back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.91,0:46:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不,你死不了\N{\ren}No, you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.02,0:47:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在送我到骷髅河之前都不会\N{\ren}Not until you get me to Skull River.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.10,0:47:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我准备好了\N{\ren}Okay. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我缝下伤口吗?\N{\ren}Would you mind stitching me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.79,0:47:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\ren}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.63,0:47:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我现在可以安心昏过去了\N{\ren}I think I'd like to pass out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.60,0:48:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,缝得不错\N{\ren}Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.00,0:48:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还是疼\N{\ren}Still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.74,0:48:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了这个\N{\ren}Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.92,0:48:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在想你朋友的事?\N{\ren}You're thinking about your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.13,0:48:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\ren}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.64,0:48:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯是个好人\N{\ren}Ross was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.04,0:49:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相识多年\N{\ren}Known him a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.08,0:49:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,玛拉\N{\ren}Mara.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.22,0:49:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让他们血债血偿\N{\ren}I'm going to kill them for what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.40,0:49:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么来荒野游荡,博伊斯?\N{\ren}Why do you travel out here, Boyce?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.11,0:49:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱城市的烟火气\N{\ren}I love the city, the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.68,0:49:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,烈酒,美食\N{\ren}A strong drink, good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.28,0:49:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有在这里才感到完整\N{\ren}Yet a part of me only feels at home here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.29,0:49:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,听风的声音\N{\ren}Listening to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.46,0:49:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看影子的舞蹈\N{\ren}Watching the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.96,0:49:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看到没,灰艾丽斯?\N{\ren}See there, Gray Alys?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.93,0:50:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,注意到光芒如何流转了吗?\N{\ren}See the way the lights shimmer and shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.34,0:50:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,盯着看久了能看出形状\N{\ren}You can see shapes in them if you look long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.51,0:50:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\ren}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.21,0:50:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真美\N{\ren}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.28,0:50:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就知道你能看懂\N{\ren}I knew you'd see.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.22,0:50:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们骨子里是一类人\N{\ren}We're alike, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.52,0:50:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,血脉相连\N{\ren}In our blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.19,0:50:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,天生就该同行\N{\ren}We're two of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.13,0:50:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼神早就出卖了你\N{\ren}I could see it in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.32,0:50:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怀上了\N{\ren}You are pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.42,0:51:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,滚吧\N{\ren}You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.77,0:51:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵聋了吗?\N{\ren}Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.00,0:51:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然聋着\N{\ren}Of course you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.11,0:51:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有继承人了\N{\ren}We have an heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.18,0:51:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这事跟你没半毛钱关系\N{\ren}Not that you had anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.71,0:51:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道新领主的爹是谁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.71,0:51:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know who the father\N{\ren}of the new Overlord is?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.19,0:51:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯\N{\ren}Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.59,0:51:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就这名字\N{\ren}That's his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.92,0:51:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,区区猎户\N{\ren}A simple hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.03,0:51:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老娘当年也是个傻白甜\N{\ren}I once was a simple girl myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.10,0:51:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢？\N{\ren}Look at me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.61,0:52:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,火车要来了\N{\ren}The train.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.08,0:53:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只能走山路,不然会被追上\N{\ren}We'll need to take the pass or they'll run us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.58,0:53:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,玩命的路\N{\ren}It'll be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.81,0:53:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,入夜后山里有恶魔游荡\N{\ren}When night falls, demons roam these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.75,0:53:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没得选\N{\ren}We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.71,0:53:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿刚正面\N{\ren}This is where we make a stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.71,0:53:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,搭把手\N{\ren}Help me with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.28,0:53:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,篝火得烧整宿\N{\ren}We need a fire all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.28,0:53:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只有火能镇住它们\N{\ren}Flame is the only thing they fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.59,0:53:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不多了\N{\ren}We don't have long.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.33,0:54:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,准备迎战\N{\ren}Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.27,0:55:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来了来了\N{\ren}Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.70,0:56:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.21,0:56:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不该\N{\ren}You should not have
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.18,0:56:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,回这鬼地方\N{\ren}come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.95,0:57:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,撒手\N{\ren}Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.42,0:57:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,博伊斯!\N{\ren}Boyce!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.08,0:57:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,救我!博伊斯!\N{\ren}Help me! Boyce!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.00,0:58:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上的火\N{\ren}The fire from your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.27,0:58:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本没感觉\N{\ren}I didn't feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.98,0:58:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,压根没温度\N{\ren}There was no fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.18,0:58:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,根本伤不了我们\N{\ren}It couldn't have hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.98,0:58:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但幻象够真就能唬住\N{\ren}But to them the illusion was real enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.78,0:58:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那你装什么痛苦?\N{\ren}Why do you suffer then?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.09,0:58:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老娘开挂是要掉血的\N{\ren}The powers I wield come at a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.79,0:58:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我听见那怪物跟你唠嗑\N{\ren}I heard the monster talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.03,0:58:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,它认得我\N{\ren}Gray Alys: He knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.57,0:58:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,八百年前的老相识\N{\ren}A long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.04,0:59:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,几个意思?\N{\ren}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.47,0:59:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方藏着大宝贝\N{\ren}There is a great treasure inside of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.44,0:59:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,屌炸天的力量\N{\ren}An immense power.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.68,0:59:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有个男人找上门\N{\ren}A man came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.38,0:59:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,贪得无厌的野心家\N{\ren}He was greedy, power hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.42,0:59:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,都这德行\N{\ren}They all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.82,0:59:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但老娘来者不拒,就帮了他\N{\ren}But I can refuse no one, so I helped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.70,0:59:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,结果这破地方有毒\N{\ren}But this place is poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.90,0:59:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方把他和手下都变成了你们看到的怪物\N{\ren}It turned him and his men into what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.87,0:59:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他本不该向我求助\N{\ren}He shouldn't have asked me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.34,0:59:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没人应该向我求助\N{\ren}No one should ever ask me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.88,0:59:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就该被世人遗忘\N{\ren}I should just be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.92,0:59:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你跟着我走\N{\ren}You're with me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.11,1:00:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,西边有踪迹\N{\ren}There are tracks to the west.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.11,1:00:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们离得很近\N{\ren}They are close.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.13,1:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,领主驾崩了\N{\ren}The Overlord is dead,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.37,1:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但王后怀有身孕!\N{\ren}but the queen is with child!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.20,1:00:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,新领主万岁!\N{\ren}All hail the new Overlord!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.92,1:00:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,领主驾崩了!\N{\ren}The Overlord is dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.59,1:01:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,新领主万岁\N{\ren}All hail the new Overlord.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.26,1:01:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,王后万岁\N{\ren}And all hail the queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.40,1:01:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,王后万岁\N{\ren}All hail the queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.33,1:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,领主与王后万岁\N{\ren}Hail the Overlord and hail the queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.14,1:01:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢大主教\N{\ren}Thank you, Patriarch.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.88,1:01:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如今我们各得所需\N{\ren}Now we both have what we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.41,1:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,您有了继承人 我得了他的权能\N{\ren}You have your heir and I have his power.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.78,1:02:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,十六年后您的子嗣才能亲政\N{\ren}16 years until your child will be of age.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.42,1:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他的权柄\N{\ren}We couldn't ask for his authority
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.52,1:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,托付给贤明之人最合适不过\N{\ren}to be in better hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.62,1:02:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您过誉了\N{\ren}You are too kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.03,1:02:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,若非大主教睿智建言与鼎力相助\N{\ren}I wouldn't have anything, Patriarch,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.40,1:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我岂能有今日成就\N{\ren}not without your wise advice and unfailing support.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.03,1:02:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 愿这份情谊永存 - 您忠实的仆人\N{\ren}- I hope that will never change. - Your loyal servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.14,1:02:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,至死不渝\N{\ren}Always.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.24,1:02:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在王座上坐着个肮脏的婊子\N{\ren}A dirty whore sits upon the throne of the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.68,1:02:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是在亵渎世间所有美好与纯洁的事物\N{\ren}An affront to all that is good and pure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.85,1:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们时间不多了\N{\ren}Our time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.55,1:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她的力量与日俱增\N{\ren}Her power grows stronger by the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.55,1:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给我找出那个女巫 拿到她的供词\N{\ren}Find me the witch. Bring me her confession.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.99,1:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,到时女巫和娼妇就一起绞死在城墙上\N{\ren}Then the witch and the whore will hang together.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.49,1:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但要快 听见没有?立刻去办!\N{\ren}But hurry. Do you hear me? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.43,1:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,明日就能抵达骷髅河\N{\ren}Tomorrow we'll reach Skull River.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.11,1:03:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他会在那里吗? - 萨尔多?\N{\ren}- Will he be there? - Sardor?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.91,1:03:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 但愿别碰上\N{\ren}I don't know. I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.78,1:03:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须独自面对他\N{\ren}I need to face him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.75,1:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那你会死\N{\ren}Then you will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.16,1:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人要死的\N{\ren}One always has to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.33,1:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你简直疯了\N{\ren}This is madness.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.77,1:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你该走了\N{\ren}You should leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.07,1:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你已完成契约\N{\ren}You did what I paid you to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.77,1:04:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当初就不该接受你的提议\N{\ren}I never should have accepted your offer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.84,1:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但你还是接了\N{\ren}But you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.18,1:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 博伊斯\N{\ren}Leave, Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.12,1:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保住性命 - 不\N{\ren}- Save yourself. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.52,1:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃吧 回头是岸\N{\ren}Forget this. Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.62,1:04:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,恕难从命\N{\ren}I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.86,1:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为何?\N{\ren}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.16,1:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我别无选择\N{\ren}Because I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.17,1:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人天生带衰 谁沾谁倒霉\N{\ren}No one should ever ask me for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.54,1:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,灰姐\N{\ren}Gray.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.98,1:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,回来\N{\ren}Come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.18,1:04:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我走\N{\ren}With me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.18,1:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还不明白吗博伊斯?\N{\ren}Don't you understand, Boyce?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.39,1:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我身上有诅咒\N{\ren}I'm cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.59,1:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近我的人都会遭殃\N{\ren}No one should ever get close to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.89,1:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,老子不在乎\N{\ren}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.41,1:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大祭司在召唤信徒了\N{\ren}The Patriarch calling to the faithful.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.42,1:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们谋划多年的时刻终于到了\N{\ren}This is the moment we've been working for.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.99,1:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,从小仰望这座城堡时\N{\ren}What we've been dreaming of since we were small,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.03,1:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就日思夜想的时刻\N{\ren}looking up at this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.40,1:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但他能轻易毁掉这一切\N{\ren}But he can take it all away from us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.86,1:05:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的亲卫现在人数占优\N{\ren}My Overwatch outnumber his men now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.93,1:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但他依然是个威胁\N{\ren}But he is still dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.81,1:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意为我做任何事吗?\N{\ren}Would you do anything for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.67,1:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,赴汤蹈火\N{\ren}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.15,1:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是我的好战士\N{\ren}You are my good soldier.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.86,1:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么突然变哑巴了？\N{\ren}Gray Alys: You're quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.86,1:06:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,前面就是骷髅河\N{\ren}Skull River lies up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.98,1:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,追兵来了\N{\ren}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.48,1:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,甩不掉他们\N{\ren}We can't outrun 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.58,1:06:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,用不着甩\N{\ren}We won't have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.61,1:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 女巫在这!- 对!\N{\ren}- The witch! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.12,1:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,属于咱们的时代终于来啦！\N{\ren}Our time is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.49,1:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,动作快!没听见吗?\N{\ren}Make haste! Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.79,1:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧的!\N{\ren}Make haste!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.86,1:07:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这次你插翅难逃!\N{\ren}You will not escape us this time!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.83,1:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城要改朝换代了\N{\ren}There will be a new day in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.54,1:07:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,妖女受死!\N{\ren}Repent, witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.42,1:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.70,1:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没了女巫助力\N{\ren}Without the witch,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.17,1:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们只能武力夺权\N{\ren}we must take the throne by force.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.24,1:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,召集我的禁卫军\N{\ren}Assemble my guard.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.25,1:08:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都聋了吗?\N{\ren}Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.82,1:08:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,弟兄们!弟兄们集合!\N{\ren}Brothers! Brothers, to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.05,1:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,省省吧 你的弟兄都死绝了\N{\ren}There is no use. Your brothers are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.09,1:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你这叛教狗贼\N{\ren}You heretic.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.43,1:08:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,以山底城守护者\N{\ren}In the name of the Overlord,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.87,1:08:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,领主之名\N{\ren}protector of the City Under The Mountain,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.64,1:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,本座宣判你 大祭司 死刑\N{\ren}I hereby sentence you, Patriarch, to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.27,1:09:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷 他到底杀了多少人?\N{\ren}Gray Alys: My God. How many has he killed?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.11,1:09:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所有反对者都被他屠尽了\N{\ren}Everyone that's come against him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.48,1:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这些痕迹\N{\ren}Look at all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.14,1:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有人住\N{\ren}Someone lives here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.55,1:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是萨尔多\N{\ren}Sardor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.05,1:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这篝火几周没生过了\N{\ren}This fire hasn't been lit in weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.53,1:10:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚月圆\N{\ren}Tonight will be the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.23,1:10:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,月圆之时他就会现身\N{\ren}He will come then.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.17,1:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回头还来得及\N{\ren}It's not too late to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.94,1:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就能走\N{\ren}We could leave now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.94,1:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为他会放我们走?\N{\ren}You think he would let us?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.51,1:10:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜他是不是正在监视我们?\N{\ren}Do you think he's not watching us?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.45,1:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以先走 我来拖住他\N{\ren}You could go. I could hold him back.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.56,1:11:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.96,1:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已经太迟了\N{\ren}It is too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.14,1:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚就是满月\N{\ren}It will be a full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.05,1:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在惦记那个女巫\N{\ren}You're still thinking about that witch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.22,1:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她向我保证过\N{\ren}She promised me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.76,1:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要她的承诺\N{\ren}You don't need what she promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.23,1:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在已经拥有一切了\N{\ren}You have everything now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.30,1:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,并非全部\N{\ren}Not everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.36,1:12:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,银器?\N{\ren}Silver?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.63,1:12:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,银器\N{\ren}Silver.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.97,1:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的武器毫无用处\N{\ren}Your weapons will be useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.24,1:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们用银器对抗过他\N{\ren}They've come against him with silver.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.14,1:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,银剑 银匕首\N{\ren}Silver swords, silver knives,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.64,1:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,镀银的箭矢\N{\ren}arrows tipped with silver.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.31,1:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都化作了尘埃\N{\ren}They're all dust now,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.18,1:12:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那些英勇的镀银战士\N{\ren}all those brave, silvered warriors.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.06,1:12:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 别这么做\N{\ren}Please, don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.96,1:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们别无选择\N{\ren}We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.83,1:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉他越来越近了 博伊斯\N{\ren}I think he's very close now, Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.84,1:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看?\N{\ren}What say you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.34,1:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还不到时候 还有时间 格雷\N{\ren}Not yet. There's still time, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.31,1:13:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,猎魔人 你在撒谎!\N{\ren}I think you lie, hunter!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.14,1:13:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没有什么萨尔多\N{\ren}There was never any Sardor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.05,1:13:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你\N{\ren}Only you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.78,1:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就知道?你知道我的真身?\N{\ren}You knew? You knew what I was?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.22,1:13:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾真心待你\N{\ren}I cared for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.63,1:13:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这么久以来你都在欺骗我\N{\ren}All this time, you tried to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.53,1:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为带我来这里\N{\ren}You thought you could bring me here
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.10,1:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就能像杀其他人那样杀我!\N{\ren}and kill me like the rest!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.37,1:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你本不该\N{\ren}You shouldn't have ever
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.51,1:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,踏足此地--灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}come here--here, Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.58,1:14:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我警告过你的\N{\ren}I tried to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.48,1:15:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呃啊!\N{\ren}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.17,1:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静\N{\ren}Calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.78,1:18:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,趁着月亮还被遮蔽 你需要休息\N{\ren}You need to rest while the moon is still covered.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.38,1:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你拥有令我嫉妒的天赋\N{\ren}You have a gift I'd kill for.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.55,1:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是否满月 你都能随心变形\N{\ren}You change at will, full moon or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.46,1:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那只是幻象\N{\ren}No. It was just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.56,1:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为了分散你的注意力 让你露出破绽\N{\ren}To distract you, to leave you vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.80,1:18:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是同类 格雷\N{\ren}We're the same, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.21,1:18:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还不明白吗?- 我明白\N{\ren}- Don't you see? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.68,1:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天生一对\N{\ren}Two of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.42,1:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你依然虚弱\N{\ren}You are still weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.99,1:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\ren}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.25,1:19:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\ren}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.29,1:19:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给我松绑\N{\ren}Untie me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.33,1:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\ren}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.93,1:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?你救了我\N{\ren}Why? You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.60,1:19:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会喜欢我的答案,博伊斯\N{\ren}You would not like my answer, Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.71,1:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是月亮作祟\N{\ren}It's the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.71,1:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕我再次变身吗?\N{\ren}Are you afraid of what'll happen if I change again?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.95,1:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你,灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}I won't harm you, Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.68,1:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在别闹 -我从未畏惧过你,猎魔人\N{\ren}- Not now. - I do not fear you, Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.49,1:19:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我太了解你了\N{\ren}I know you too well.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.06,1:19:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这一路上我摸清了你的所有弱点\N{\ren}I learned all your weaknesses along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.29,1:19:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还给你新增了几个\N{\ren}I even added to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.00,1:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么鬼话?\N{\ren}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.80,1:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉\N{\ren}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.27,1:20:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但当你遇见我时,命运就已注定\N{\ren}But your fate was sealed when you met me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.73,1:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对,博伊斯\N{\ren}You were right, Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.33,1:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,银制武器确实不够看\N{\ren}Silver weapons were not enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.27,1:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我下毒了?\N{\ren}You poisoned me?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.17,1:20:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,必须让银元素融入你的血液\N{\ren}I had to put silver in your blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.51,1:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你当初就该让我死透\N{\ren}Why didn't you just let me die?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.15,1:20:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为死物毫无利用价值\N{\ren}Because dead things have no power.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.02,1:20:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,等等,等等!\N{\ren}Hey, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.52,1:21:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你--你必须实现我的愿望\N{\ren}You--you have to grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.29,1:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"来者不拒"可是你的原话\N{\ren}You can refuse no one. Those are your words.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.16,1:21:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想要什么,博伊斯? -我要你\N{\ren}- What do you wish for, Boyce? - I want you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.40,1:21:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我们永远在一起\N{\ren}I want us to be together.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.34,1:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,并肩狩猎,共同战斗\N{\ren}I want us to hunt together, to fight together.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.34,1:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,终结这该死的孤独?\N{\ren}To find an end to all this loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.01,1:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的,你也渴望如此,我知道\N{\ren}Yes, you want it, too, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.45,1:21:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我向来有求必应\N{\ren}I refuse no one.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.42,1:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但需要付出代价\N{\ren}But there is a price to be paid.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.72,1:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管开口,任何代价\N{\ren}Name it. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.72,1:21:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\ren}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.43,1:24:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,女巫回来了!\N{\ren}The witch is back!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.34,1:24:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是她!就是她!\N{\ren}Man 2: It's her! It's her!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.84,1:24:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-她回来了!-她回来了!那个女巫!\N{\ren}- She's back! - She's back! The witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.11,1:24:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,绞不死的女巫!\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.11,1:24:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,绞不死的女巫!\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.31,1:24:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,绞不死的女巫!\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.15,1:24:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我回去干活!\N{\ren}Get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.52,1:24:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,绞不死的女巫!\N{\ren}The witch that will not hang!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.63,1:24:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-绞不死的女巫!-打倒领主!\N{\ren}- The witch that will not hang! - Down with the Overlord!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.30,1:24:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,推翻圣教会!\N{\ren}Down with the Church!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.66,1:24:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒领主!\N{\ren}Down with the Overlord!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.17,1:24:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,推翻圣教会!\N{\ren}Down with the Church!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.17,1:24:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒领主!推翻圣教会!\N{\ren}Down with the Overlord! Down with the Church!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.54,1:24:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒领主!\N{\ren}Down with the Overlord!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.04,1:24:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,推翻圣教会!\N{\ren}Down with the Church!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.87,1:25:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着这个\N{\ren}Gray Alys: Take this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.51,1:25:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,让女王割破手指\N{\ren}Tell the queen to cut herself,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.38,1:25:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,将鲜血滴在皮甲上再穿上\N{\ren}to drip her own blood onto the skin and wear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.95,1:25:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今夜月相即将圆满\N{\ren}Tonight will be the end of the lunar cycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.01,1:25:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她必须在午夜前完成仪式\N{\ren}She must do it before the end of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.08,1:25:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,届时力量将归她所有\N{\ren}Then the power will be hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.19,1:25:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,狼皮?\N{\ren}Wolf skin?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.36,1:25:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在巢穴中被猎杀的变形者之皮\N{\ren}The skin of a shapeshifter killed in its lair.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.69,1:25:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 灰艾丽斯 你完成了女王的委托\N{\ren}Well, Gray Alys, you have done what she asked of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.06,1:25:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,却辜负了我的信任\N{\ren}but you have failed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.73,1:25:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我付钱买的是结果\N{\ren}I did not pay you for success.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.93,1:25:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 把怀表还给我\N{\ren}Now, give me my timepiece back.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.40,1:25:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 杰雷斯 这是我应得的\N{\ren}No, Jerais. I've earned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.07,1:25:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的要求并未达成\N{\ren}But I did not get what I asked for.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.14,1:25:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可你得到了想要的东西\N{\ren}But you got what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.94,1:25:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么东西? - 女王本人\N{\ren}- And what is that? - The queen herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.55,1:25:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有个男人 她孩子的父亲\N{\ren}There was a man, the father of her child.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.05,1:25:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你觊觎王座 却视他为绊脚石\N{\ren}You wanted her, but knew he stood in your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.96,1:26:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你解决了这个麻烦\N{\ren}I have changed that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.13,1:26:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那人是谁?\N{\ren}Who was this man?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.50,1:26:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什么名字?\N{\ren}What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.60,1:26:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫博伊斯\N{\ren}His name was Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.97,1:26:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.64,1:26:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她杀了博伊斯!\N{\ren}She killed Boyce!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.11,1:26:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不 求求你\N{\ren}No, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.15,1:26:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本不该如此\N{\ren}It could never have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.79,1:26:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么?\N{\ren}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.29,1:26:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他是头野兽\N{\ren}He was a beast.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.03,1:26:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,野兽?\N{\ren}Beast?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.10,1:26:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你对野兽又了解多少?\N{\ren}What do you know of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.13,1:26:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他腐蚀了你 你变了\N{\ren}He twisted you. You changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.80,1:26:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是你策划了这一切\N{\ren}You did this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.10,1:26:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是做了该做的事 我在保护你\N{\ren}I did what I had to do. I protected you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.54,1:26:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你背叛了我 - 不 不是的 我...\N{\ren}- You betrayed me. - No, no. I--
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.68,1:26:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你派人杀了他 我孩子的父亲!\N{\ren}You had him killed. The father of my child!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.78,1:27:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\ren}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.39,1:27:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 求求你 - 不!\N{\ren}- Please. - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.45,1:27:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿为你做任何事\N{\ren}I would do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.16,1:27:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就为我去死\N{\ren}Then die for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.33,1:27:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我做这些全是为了你 博伊斯\N{\ren}I did this for you, Boyce.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.17,1:27:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我们能长相厮守 并肩狩猎\N{\ren}So we could be together, hunt together.
