Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.45,1:28:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒领主!\N{\ren}Down with the Overlord!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.50,1:30:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 我的故事精彩吗?\N{\ren}So, how'd you like my story?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.90,1:30:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,结局还没想好呢\N{\ren}I still don't know how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.50,1:30:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,或许该让你尝尝活剥的滋味\N{\ren}Maybe with me skinning you alive,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.34,1:30:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你当初剥我的皮那样\N{\ren}just like you did to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.08,1:30:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这个结局我可不太喜欢\N{\ren}I'm not sure I like that ending.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.52,1:30:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜啊\N{\ren}Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.72,1:30:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我早知道你是女王的姘头\N{\ren}I knew you were the queen's lover.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.02,1:30:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别急着走嘛 - 你清楚我的底细\N{\ren}- Don't leave yet. - You know what I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.69,1:30:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能留在这 - 你说过唯一能让你\N{\ren}- I can't stay here. - You said the only woman
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.56,1:30:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真心相爱的女人必须与你同类\N{\ren}you could truly love would be someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.66,1:30:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不是那种人 - 若我能变成呢?\N{\ren}- You are not that. - But what if I could be?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.76,1:30:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你赐我化身为兽的力量,灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}I want from you the power to become a beast, Gray Alys.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.17,1:30:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我从不拒绝任何人 - 我要你辜负她\N{\ren}- I refuse no one. - I want you to fail her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.51,1:30:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我从不拒绝任何人 - 我要的是你\N{\ren}- I refuse no one. - I want you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.24,1:30:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不拒绝任何人\N{\ren}I refuse no one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.55,1:30:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我早预见女王的欲望\N{\ren}Gray Alys: I knew that the queen's desires
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.35,1:30:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,终将引发革命\N{\ren}would lead to revolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.18,1:30:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她永远得不到你的皮毛\N{\ren}And that she would never wear your skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.12,1:31:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我早知你会活着\N{\ren}I knew you would live.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.46,1:31:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在撒谎\N{\ren}You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.96,1:31:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我早知道这把枪会卡壳\N{\ren}Just like I know that'll misfire.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.14,1:31:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,世人都说只要找灰艾丽斯\N{\ren}They say you can buy anything you might desire
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.74,1:31:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就能买到任何渴望之物...\N{\ren}from Gray Alys...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.78,1:31:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...但最好别这么做\N{\ren}...but it is better not to.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.62,1:31:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这不正是我们想要的吗?\N{\ren}And isn't this what we wished for?

